{"tid":1843261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無人理】公共關係科跳過傳媒，自己開傳媒直播，其實好大獲","createTime":"2020-01-26T06:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T11:49:33.000Z","uid":228995,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9b52cd453700f04e57b75f9ac04f58444a68c6","tid":1843261,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:29:01.000Z","msg":"//晚上近11時，防暴警於撤退時向傳媒擲手擲式催淚彈，有人向警車扔雜物。有街坊指，防暴警落車後僅舉黑旗1秒，之後就手擲催淚彈。而同步在facebook直播的警察公共關係科（PPRB）人員，則避開所有催淚彈畫面。在附近街頭擺擋的持牌熟食檔主紛向傳媒抱怨，警方在年初一都放TG趕客，現場有小朋友又有老人家，批評警方不是，反問「係咪唔使做生意？」女檔主又指，她們是合法擺檔，獲准擺賣至年初三，警方反斥她是「搞事分子」，「仲攞胡椒噴霧對住我哋呀」。她慨嘆食材遭TG污染，不能再出售，即時損失過千元。<br />\n<br />\n在警民衝突爆發前，售賣白酒牛油金菇的阿K表示，雖然今年有肺炎及示威活動影響，但生意額反而比去年更好，人旺丁又旺財，「賣到唔夠貨&hellip;&hellip; 我覺得今年百花齊放咗， 以前比較多遊客齋睇唔買，但而家多咗真正香港人去幫趁。」他又說，暫時沒有警察或食環署職員前來干預，氣氛大致和平。阿K在招牌上貼上「連豬」等卡通，被問到是否想藉此宣揚一下政治理念，他笑言「大家明㗎啦，明嘅人就會明，唔明嘅人永遠都唔明。」他又強調新年夜巿是本土文化，希望香港人能一直保留下去。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200126/HZLVK2UQKPZTVT32U66HPUZ574/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200126%2FHZLVK2UQKPZTVT32U66HPUZ574%2F&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGej%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=c0efdf10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200126%2FHZLVK2UQKPZTVT32U66HPUZ574%2F&h=7a987753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200126/HZLVK2UQKPZTVT32U66HPUZ574/</a><br />\n<br />\n仲要自己做埋旁白，以爲自己真係記者<br />\n<br />\n其實呢件事象徵意義好大<br />\n極權主義又再進一步<br />\n<br />\n今日克警可以示威現場做直播<br />\n代表下次示威集會就算係有申請不反<br />\n對方大可以安排幾個人做live，行近每個參加者close shot大頭<br />\n<br />\n再下一次可能就執法時做大龍鳳開直播<br />\n證明新一哥好大喜功"},{"pid":"ce111e3db4c25ce0d33010cbf96cd6aba7678580","tid":1843261,"uid":75591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:48:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830b7addafa594148c3e0a169fbef0e682d2f1d6","tid":1843261,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"0991963a426153323c9fcb957d3d3a3db5dfae9c","tid":1843261,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:52:04.000Z","msg":"只會搞到更多人唔信警隊"},{"pid":"052177b2549a484729fc24f178d3315a28466493","tid":1843261,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9c6aad3c4a36e61e1d73ca4443da159fb923ef75","tid":1843261,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1e2218feaf52d6e81ae97933b9054b187498a8","tid":1843261,"uid":147721,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"新憲法要寫明 執法部門及執法人員（無論執勤定休班）不得從事傳媒行為"},{"pid":"bae000c9a296752644c41b76be0cac1117126ba7","tid":1843261,"uid":109999,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:58:55.000Z","msg":"除非好似老彭咁對北愛爾蘭咁徹底解散重組<br />\n唔係我一世都唔會信香港警察"},{"pid":"188000aefe5ec976894d70d5abd52bd02febd761","tid":1843261,"uid":237465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"經邊個, 都冇人信 恐怖分子的說話  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq70aOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq70aOE.jpg&h=84a3d903&s={S